member.name: T:QuestRSX.TranslationHelper
member.summary: Helper class for text translation.

member.name: M:QuestRSX.TranslationHelper.TranslateText(System.String,System.String,System.String)
member.summary: Translates the specified text from the source language to the target language.
member.remarks: This method uses the Azure Cognitive Services Translator API to perform the translation. The detected language of the input text and the confidence score are logged for debugging purposes.
member.param: The text to be translated. Cannot be null or empty.
The language code of the source text (e.g., "en" for English). This parameter is currently unused and may be ignored.
The language code of the target language (e.g., "pl" for Polish). Must be a valid language code supported by the translation service.
member.returns: The translated text as a string. Returns an empty string if the translation fails or no translation is available.
